      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, offering precise shift throws and a direct mechanical connection. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and structural subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis longevity. The factory limited-slip differential provides predictable lock-up, while the suspension has been enhanced with Bilstein dampers for improved damping profiles. While the exterior shows honest patina from enthusiast use, the drivetrain remains exceptionally healthy with strong compression across all cylinders. A true driver\u2019s car with sorted internals and sharp turn-in characteristics.",
